lyrics:
f = do; BL 103

1. Porini dong maribu hali, paraloling ni sorangkin
Bois ni gogoh inggananni, mamuji Naibatanta in,
Ibaen malasni uhurhin, hinorhon ni pambaen-Ni in.

2. Ai ambit ondos ma sorangku, bai ujung ni dunia on,
sagala jolma arahonku, mamuji Naibata tongtong;
Talup do gok ni uhurhin, hubaen pasangap Tuhan in.

3. Ulang ma modom ho tonduyhu, sai puho ho, sai hehe ma;
Pongkut ma ho bani horjamu, sai puji Tuhan Naibata;
Sai baen ma gok ni pandeimin, laho mamuji Tuhan in.

4. Tarima kasih ma uhurhu, Bamu o Naibata tongtong;
Ibahen dearni layak-Mu, binere-Mu hubangku on;
Ai ipatudu Ham tongtong ganup na porlu bangku on.

5. Hupuji pakon Ham, o Jesus, ibaen parholong ateiMu.
Mardingat darohMu madurus, pakon ganupan layak-Mu;
Mambahen haluahon on, hubai pardousa banggal on.

6. Ham pe homa, Tonduy Napansing, sai jalo Ham ma dodingkon;
Margogoh anjaha matunggung do Ham, mangapoh uhurhon;
Ia hubaen na dear in, halani gogoh-Mu do in.

7. Ai ise do mamasu-masu, au on o Naibata, lang Ham?
Pamatang rap pakon tonduyhu, sai iparmudu-mudu Ham
Jaha lumbang uhur-Mu in mangidah pardousaonkin.

8. Sai layakMu do pujionku sadokah na manggoluh au;
Sai Goran-Mu pasangaponku sadokah na marhosah au
Ronsi rotap ni hosahkin, sai pujionku Ham ijin.

9. Sai jalo ma, ale Tuhanku, pamujingkon na hurang in;
Paima das au on hu surga, ianan na gok dear in,
Marlaksa hali ma ijin, dodingkononku Tuhankin.

do = es

1. Sai na margantih tahun on sonin rosi magira
Jesus baen ham uhurhon ase tongtong marhira
Bai parsurutni ajalhin, janah manimbang ujungnin.

2. Iudut Ham do hosahkin paidah-idah ahu,
Atap na dong do buah ni horja-Mu in hu bangku;
Hape gati hiranan Ham: Buah ni in seng jumpah Ham

3. Ra ma manringis Naibata mangidah parlahouhu;
Ra ihatahon: “Roboh ma haron na so behangku;
Seng ongga ra marbuah in, benaha be marguna in!”
4. Halani kinahuhon-Mu do au, ase manggoloh;
Sonon nimu bai Bapa-Mu: Paturut ma manggoloh;
Haron, holong ma atei-Mu, taun roh pe das uhum-Mu.

5. O Jesus, au urupi ma bai tahun on mamboan,
Buah na ramos, na tama, padaoh ma hamagouan,
Sai Ham pagogoh au tongtong, pasangap Ham bai goluhkon.

do=c; BL 84

1. Ise do ganup sidea i lambung ni Naibata;
Marsotali do hudidah marsinalsal do homa.
Ganup do mandoding bei sai riap mamuji bei.

2. In ma da, na dob maluah, halak na tongon bujur.
Hasomanta na martuah na porsaya in botul.
Bai Tuhanta Jesus in, na mangkopkop hita on.

3. Na maparngit, tinaronni, sanggah na i tanoh on;
Na sombuh na sain dokahni, gabe hasangapon do.
In do rupei nin nuan, malas uhurnin ibaen.

4. Na mandoding do sidea pasangapkon Jesus in;
Na tangkas ijin ididah sintong ni Hata-Ni in.
Na pinarbagah-Ni in, ondos do ganupan in.

5. Seng be hona bai sidea sambor ni dunia on;
Seng be dong ijin taridah sisunsahi hita on;
‘Ge ganup dousanta pe, seng dingaton be hape.

6. Horah, lohei, ampa loja, ‘ge borgoh ni ari in.
Porkas, longgur, haba-haba, udan, milas ari in;
Uhum bani dousa in, seng be hona in hujin.

7. Ai bai Naibata sidea, si pasabaou uhur in;
Jesus do tongtong ididah i nagori atas in;
Hatuahon do ijin sadokah-dokahni in.

8. Tuhan Jesus, Rajanami na marholong atei in.
Sasap Ham ma dousanami, jolom tangannami on!
Haganup na ijon, sai pamasuk use on.

do = as

1. Tatap hanai on na humpul ijon
Sihol do pujion nami layak-Mu o Tuhannami.
Tatap hanai on na humpul ijon.

2. Togu hanai on, na mardousa on;
Ale Jesus Tuhannami, sai maidop ham bannami.
Togu ham tongtong na mardousa on.

3. Sai parorot Ham, ganup hanai on;
Humbai ganup munsuh nami, ulang magou be hanami;
Sai parorot Ham, ganup hanai on.

4. Sai urasi Ham ganup hanai on;
As mubah uhurnami, sai borsih ma tonduynami.
Sai urasi Ham ganup hanai on.

5. Sai ajari ham ganup hanai on;
’Se ganup botohonnami dalan sidalanannami.
Sai ajari ham ganup hanai on.

6. Sai pintori ham ganup hanai on;
Sai unduk ma uhurnami mansopotkon dousanami.
Sai pintori ham ganup hanai on.

7. Sai pamasuk Ham ganup hanai on;
Ulang modom be hanami bani pardousaon nami.
Sai puhoi Ham ganup hanai on.

8. Sai pamasuk ham ganup hanai on;
Bai na jumlah ajalnami anggo bois bohalnami.
Sai pamasuk Ham das hu surga in.

do = bes; 4 ketuk; BL 196

1. Roh ham bai Jesus, roh ham botul, tangar hata-Ni jalo bujur.
Na roh do Jesus pagoluh ham, asal porsaya ham.
Malas do uhurta in use, ai borsih hun bani dousa pe;
Sai roh ma hita hu surga in, ai sonang do ijin.

2. Roh ham bai Jesus, akuhon ma, pambahenanmu na so tama;
Sai sasapon-Ni dousamu in, ibaen daroh-Ni in;
Malas do uhurta in use, ai borsih hun bani dousa pe;
Sai roh ma hita hu surga in, ai sonang do ijin.

3. Roh ham bai Jesus, papodas ma, ai seng ra Ia manulak ham;
Parholong atei do Jesus in, tenger ma uhurmu;
Malas do uhurta in use, ai borsih hun bani dousa pe;
Sai roh ma hita hu surga in, ai sonang do ijin.

4. Roh ham bai Jesus, ai holong do, uhur-Ni bani halak na roh ;
Ai ipaluah tonduyta in, ulang be magou in.
Malas do uhurta in use, ai borsih hun bani dousa pe;
Sai roh ma hita hu surga in, ai sonang do ijin.

do = bes; BL 24

1. Haholongan na mapansing humbai Jesus Tuhankin;
Sai sogopi sai masuki uhur pakon tonduyhin.

2. Malas uhur ni na sonang i nagori atas in;
Sai palamlam, sai pasonang siholhin, o Jesuskin.

3. Hasonangan, hadameian, na roh humbai Jesus in;
Sai pahosah au na loja, ase jorei uhurhin.

4. Sai palumbang Ham uhurhu, bai ganup hasomankin;
Ase sai ringgas uhurhu, lao manasap dousaniin.

5. Habasaron, hadameion, naroh humbani Jesus in;
Goki uhur pakon tonduy, ulang mosor in hunjin.

6. Haholongan humbai Jesus, sai parborsih uhurhon.
Tong sai usir ganup tikas, ‘se borsih tong tonduyhon.

7. Halaniin, Ham Naibatangku, sai pagomos uhurhin;
Ase ondos au hu lambung ni ganup na monang in.

do = g; BL 163

1. Mardalan au sonari, hu hasonangan in.
Sai lambin roh dohorni, au on bai ari in.
Humbai na daoh huidah, lihar ianan in.
Sai sonang do sidea, na dob ondos hujin.

2. Buei do halilian i tongah dalan in;
Podas do au mardalan hu hasonangan in.
Buei do hasunsahan na manlioti au;
Hubontas parmaraan, mardingat Jesus au.

3. Itompas milas ari ijomba udan au;
Hotop huhabiari na mangonggopi au;
Matangku sai manatap bai situjuankin;
Ganup na huparsinta, sirsir i surga in.

4. Malas tumang uhurhu, ’ge hanar imbangkin;
Sai Jesus hasomanku, baen hatundalankin.
Sai Ia do manogu arian, borngin pe;
Tenger tumang uhurhu, hu surga au use.

5. Hugolom bai uhurhu silang ni Tuhankin;
Sai in sijolomanku, sai in haposankin;
Ai domma saud itobus Tuhanku tonduyhin;
Ai Ia do paondos hu surga langkahkin.

6. Tenger tumang uhurhu bai pardalanankin;
’Ge bois pe hosahku, sai ondos au hujin;
’Ge loja ari-ari bai pardagangan on,
Hape santongkin nari sai sonang au tongtong.

do = es; BL 111

1. Na botoh dohor ni ajalhu? Aringku lao bodari roh.
Ai ambit roh sompongtingkingku parpudi in, na botoh do?
Jesus Jesus ibahen daroh-Mu in pasonang Ham parmateihin.

2. Gati legan bai bod ni an marimbang bai sogod ni in;
Ai sanggah au ijon mansari sai tong jagaon ajalhin
Jesus, Jesus, ibaen daroh-Mu in, pasonang Ham parmateihin.

3. Ajari Ham au, o Tuhanku lao mamingkiri ajalhin;
Singatkon Ham ma bai uhurhu parmatei-Mu o Jesuskin.
Jesus Jesus ibahen daroh-Mu in pasonang Ham parmateihin.

4. Urupi Ham au pasirsirhon langkahku na i tanoh on;
Paingat Ham au mamberehon Bamu, Tuhanku, uhurhon.
Jesus Jesus ibahen daroh-Mu in pasonang Ham parmateihin.

5. Lambin masihol au hu surga tundalhononku tanoh on.
Sai huparayak dompak surga sadokah au i tanoh on;
Jesus Jesus ibahen daroh-Mu in pasonang Ham parmateihin.

6. Sai sasap Ham ganup dousangku marhitei-hitei daroh-Mu.
In ma hubaen gabe hiouhu marayak hasonangan in.
Jesus Jesus ibahen daroh-Mu in pasonang Ham parmateihin.

7. Padihut au Bamu, o Jesus, uhurhu tong bai uhur-Mu;
Huja pe Ham sai tong au dihut ijon age i surga-Mu;
Jesus Jesus ibahen daroh-Mu in pasonang Ham parmateihin.

8. Age sompong roh hamateian sadarion ge patar pe;
Seng habiaran be tanoman dob Jesus rupeihin hape;
Jesus Jesus ibahen daroh-Mu in pasonang Ham parmateihin.

9. On pe sonang ma au manggoluh, matei pe au sonang
Hubotoh ipagoluh Jesus au humbai hamateiankin;
Jesus Jesus ibahen daroh-Mu in pasonang Ham parmateihin.

do = g; BL 177

1. Songon ursa na binuru sai horahan bai bah in
Sai sonai do au mangindo sol darngos bai Tuhankin.
Sal horahan tonduyhin Bamu ale Tuhankin.
Ai antigan idahonku bohi-Mu ale Tuhanku

2. Iluh-ihuh ni matangku, sai hupangan do tongtong;
Ai sal tong nini munsuhku; “Ai ija Naibatamu?”
Sai marhoru uhurhin ai hudingat parrohkin.
Ronsi lurlur ni dodingku lao hu rumah ni Tuhanku

3. Undukmin, ale tonduyhu mase pala rusak ho?
Hatengerhon Naibatamu, ai paluahon-Ni do
Ho na marhoru nuan, malas uhurmin ibaen;
Ase tong pasangaponmu Goran ni partuahonmu.

4. Sai manrogop do uhurhu sanggah bai na tangis au;
Jordan do habuanganku ampa Hermon in, na daoh;
Songon bah sampuran in mompas bai tondolannin.
Sai sonai do mangkamompas parlajouan in hu bangku.

5. Iparbagah Naibatangku idop ni uhur-Ni in;
Jadi malas ma uhurhu anggo sai hudingat in;
Borngin, ge arian in hudodingkon do ijin;
Dear layak ni Jahowa mangurupi kuria-Ni.

6. Ham, alo Batar-batarhu, seng ingaton-Mu be au?
Ai sai tambah do honingku, iapasi munsuh au;
Ai holi-holingku pe, sal maropuk do hape;
Ai sai tong nini munsuhku;”Ai ija ma Naibatamu?”
7. Undukmin ale tonduyhu, mase ma sai rusak ho?
Hatengerhon ma Tuhanmu seng tadingkonon-Ni ho;
Pujionku do tongtong Naibata bai goluhkon.
Hatuahon ni bohingku, sai tongtong do haposanku.
